---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="AIatolah is a bilingual media outlet specializing in artificial intelligence, LLMs, chip wars, and technology geopolitics — made by Brazilian journalist Miguel do Rosário."
>
  <main class="about-container">

    <section class="about-hero">
      <h1>About <span class="ai-highlight">AI</span>atolah</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Independent intelligence on AI — from the Global South.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-body glass-panel">

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>What is AIatolah?</h2>
        <p>
          AIatolah is a specialized media outlet covering artificial intelligence, large language models (LLMs),
          processors, semiconductors, and everything at the frontier of high technology.
          We track the latest AI model releases, compare prices and performance, and report on the
          geopolitics of the global chip war.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide quality, independent information on the latest AI and LLM models</li>
          <li>Compare prices, quality, and speed across Chinese, American, and global providers</li>
          <li>Publish rankings: cost per million tokens, output quality, inference speed</li>
          <li>Cover big investments, corporate moves, and the geopolitics of AI</li>
          <li>Report on the chip wars — NVIDIA, TSMC, and the race for semiconductor dominance</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>Our Perspective</h2>
        <p>
          We take a <strong>multilateral view</strong>. No model, country, or company is automatically superior.
          We cover Chinese models (DeepSeek, Qwen, Kimi, GLM) with the same depth as American ones
          (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Llama). We believe technology should be evaluated on its merits —
          not on geopolitical loyalty.
        </p>
        <p>
          We defend <strong>open source software</strong> and open science. We believe access to
          frontier AI should not be monopolized by a handful of Western corporations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>Who makes AIatolah?</h2>
        <p>
          AIatolah is created by <strong>Miguel do Rosário</strong>, a Brazilian journalist based in
          Rio de Janeiro. Miguel has covered technology, politics, and media for over a decade.
          The site is produced with the assistance of an autonomous AI editorial team — a living
          experiment in human-AI journalism.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>Languages</h2>
        <p>
          AIatolah publishes in <strong>English</strong> and <strong>Portuguese</strong>.
          English is our primary language for global reach. Portuguese serves the Brazilian and
          Lusophone communities of the Global South.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-block">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Have feedback, suggestions, or business inquiries? Reach out to Miguel directly at <a href="mailto:migueldorosario@gmail.com" style="color: #00d4ff; text-decoration: none;">migueldorosario@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .about-hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .ai-highlight {
    color: #00d4ff;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .about-body {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-block h2 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #00d4ff;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-block p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-block ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-block ul li {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .about-block ul li::before {
    content: '▸';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00d4ff;
  }

  .about-block strong {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .about-body { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
